### Tracking API Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Record a user click
POST {{baseUrl}}/tracking/click
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "business_id": "ChIJN1t_tDeuEmsRUsoyG83frY4",
  "lat": 37.7749,
  "lng": -122.4194
}

###

### 2. Record user location (typically on login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tracking/location
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lat": 37.7749,
  "lng": -122.4194,
  "city": "San Francisco",
  "state": "California", 
  "country": "USA"
}

###

### 3. Get user's click history
GET {{baseUrl}}/tracking/clicks?limit=10&skip=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Get user's location history
GET {{baseUrl}}/tracking/locations?limit=10&skip=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Get clicks for specific business
GET {{baseUrl}}/tracking/clicks/business/ChIJN1t_tDeuEmsRUsoyG83frY4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Get user's current city (from latest location)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tracking/current-city
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###